{"id": 2527, "genre": 1001, "title": "约会/聚会就餐，你都遇到过哪些困扰？", "description": "入座、点餐、结账全是技术活，一想到要跟一群人吃饭就自动进入备战状态。", "record_count": 3356, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180917172915ZE8VMTCg97mKDjAs.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-09-30T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 308736, "content": "能不聚餐坚决不聚餐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1492750}, {"id": 301570, "content": "和许久未见的兄弟吃饭，不知道谁买单，即使双方关系十分要好", "image": null, "praise_count": 136, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1435885}, {"id": 301572, "content": "个人觉得是饮食习惯   比如重庆就吃的特辣特麻   可能有些地方就吃的清淡或者甜腻些", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1099752}, {"id": 301573, "content": "冷场", "image": null, "praise_count": 688, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1363163}, {"id": 301830, "content": "牙齿上有辣椒皮？？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1458866}, {"id": 301575, "content": "吃完饭又忘带纸，嘴是油的", "image": null, "praise_count": 89, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1457417}, {"id": 301831, "content": "一个都不认识，还要装作聊的很投机。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 197974}, {"id": 301832, "content": "讨厌烟味儿！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208827}, {"id": 301577, "content": "不喜欢也不会敬酒，不会玩儿酒桌游戏，如何变成隐形人？", "image": null, "praise_count": 526, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216775}, {"id": 302346, "content": "没有利益的同学关系。会来事儿的不断给混的好的各种拍马，各种倒酒夹菜。好像不是AA制似的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 882352}, {"id": 301835, "content": "遇到自己喜欢吃的菜，却不好意思一直夹", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1458877}, {"id": 299020, "content": "点餐的时候遇到对方说“随便”", "image": null, "praise_count": 310, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 299021, "content": "多人聚餐，不知道点几道菜合适", "image": null, "praise_count": 79, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 301581, "content": "简单点，我就是我", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1457436}, {"id": 305933, "content": "吃的少 花的多", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1479134}, {"id": 299022, "content": "吃西餐全都遵照西式用餐习惯，会担心被嘲笑「装腔作势，有文化自卑」", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 301582, "content": "点菜时:随便，都行，你喜欢...", "image": null, "praise_count": 45, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1457432}, {"id": 299023, "content": "跟长辈吃饭会担心座次，哪儿是上座", "image": null, "praise_count": 71, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 301583, "content": "每人点一道菜的话点什么……", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 411759}, {"id": 301839, "content": "点餐认真问一遍说都可以，菜上来了说都不可以", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 312376}, {"id": 301585, "content": "一堆菜大家都不怎么吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1418546}, {"id": 301841, "content": "几个熟悉一些的老自己聊 互相不太熟的别凉在一边玩手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 404676}, {"id": 302865, "content": "别人点的菜都不爱吃，但是还要装着好吃的样子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1466010}, {"id": 301586, "content": "没座", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 636017}, {"id": 301587, "content": "与不熟的人吃饭很煎熬，不知道聊些什么，就一直吃。", "image": null, "praise_count": 261, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1457319}, {"id": 301590, "content": "跟老板一起吃饭的时候，不知聊什么好？尬聊..", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1206167}, {"id": 301846, "content": "尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1446282}, {"id": 301592, "content": "想着如何能够睡到对方( ¯ᒡ̱¯ )و", "image": null, "praise_count": 136, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1262336}, {"id": 312600, "content": "沒有話題，超低級惡俗的主題，不想說話", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1510858}, {"id": 301849, "content": "紧张到想放屁", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1458945}, {"id": 301850, "content": "  别人聊什么房子，孩子，对于我这个单身狗来说完全插不上嘴，尴尬到同事一脸歉意的问我是不是很无聊，聚餐不如在家里喝凉水", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 545614}, {"id": 303130, "content": "全是自己不熟的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1467058}, {"id": 301851, "content": "入座点餐上菜开吃吃完擦嘴结账", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1456595}, {"id": 301596, "content": "装斯文 没吃饱", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1362098}, {"id": 301597, "content": "到底看不看手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1457494}, {"id": 301853, "content": "说好的轮流点餐，结果变成了一个人点餐", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1106598}, {"id": 301598, "content": "随便，然后你点了，她又说不好吃，或者垮着脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 80, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1455292}, {"id": 301854, "content": "就我一个人在张罗，其他人都在看手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1458882}, {"id": 301600, "content": "老板说，某某你去负责点菜……", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1050868}, {"id": 301856, "content": "9个女的就我一个男的，男的aa女的免费", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 693756}, {"id": 301601, "content": "为什么有些人就是要在别人店里吃饭时候大声说”他们弄的菜一点也不好吃，下次我们不要来了”我每次都觉得好尴尬啊，你说别人手艺不行不能等你出来以后说嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 89, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1455292}, {"id": 301858, "content": "喜欢的菜够不着 就不吃了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 213698}, {"id": 301859, "content": "-吃什么\n-随你\n-那我点了\n-我想吃这个，刚才咋不点", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1459007}, {"id": 301604, "content": "餐桌游戏惩罚无节制，还美曰其名为增进感情。", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1457505}, {"id": 301862, "content": "长辈或者老师来这桌敬酒", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1459031}, {"id": 301863, "content": "敬酒，不管是家庭聚餐还是同事聚餐，敬酒的规矩不懂也不想懂也不想去敬", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 952312}, {"id": 301608, "content": "要么是自己哔哔哔说一大堆别人不回应 要么是有些局促不知道该说什么好看别人一直哔哔哔 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 822606}, {"id": 301864, "content": "尬聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1456215}, {"id": 302376, "content": "不会聊天", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1462765}, {"id": 301609, "content": "尬聊，傻笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1457521}]}